  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/hiddriverkit\/alphanumeric-display-enum\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T10:36:41Z\n---\n\n# Alphanumeric Display\n\n**API Collection**\n\nUsages for alphanumeric displays on consumer devices.\n\n## Getting the Usages\n\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_ASCIICharacterSet**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_AlphanumericDisplay**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_CharacterHeight**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_CharacterReport**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_CharacterSpacingHorizontal**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_CharacterSpacingVertical**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_CharacterWidth**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_ClearDisplay**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_Column**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_Columns**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_CursorBlink**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_CursorEnable**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_CursorMode**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_CursorPixelPositioning**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_CursorPositionReport**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_DataReadBack**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_DisplayAttributesReport**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_DisplayControlReport**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_DisplayData**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_DisplayEnable**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_DisplayStatus**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_ErrFontdatacannotberead**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_ErrNotaloadablecharacter**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_FontData**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_FontReadBack**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_FontReport**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_HorizontalScroll**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_Reserved**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_Row**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_Rows**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_ScreenSaverDelay**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_ScreenSaverEnable**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_StatNotReady**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_StatReady**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_UnicodeCharacterSet**\n- **kHIDUsage_AD_VerticalScroll**\n\n## Devices\n\n- **Generic Device Controls**: Usages associated with generic types of device information, such as battery level.\n- **Keyboard or Keypad**: Usages related to keyboard and keypad devices.\n- **LEDs**: Usages related to the LEDs and other indicators on the device.\n- **Buttons**: Usages for devices that contain user-selectable controls.\n- **Ordinals**: Usages for custom-defined behaviors on a device.\n- **Telephony**: Usages for telephony devices, including telephone keypads and answering machines.\n- **Consumer**: Usages for app-specific controls on consumer devices, such as clocks, TVs, and audio equipment.\n- **Digitizer**: Usages for digitizer devices, such as styluses and touch screens.\n- **Physical Interface Device**: Usages for devices with actuators or other physical interfaces.\n- **Haptics**\n- **FIDO**\n- **Braille Device**\n\n",
